      <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;about-me&#34;&gt;About Me&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Beginning in Fall 2025, I will be joining &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.ramapo.edu&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Ramapo College of New Jersey&lt;/a&gt; as a Visiting Assistant Professor of Mathematics. I received my Bachelor&amp;rsquo;s degree in Mathematics in 2015 from &lt;a href=&#34;https://ramjas.du.ac.in/college/web/index.php?r=department/department-of-mathematics&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Ramjas College, University of Delhi&lt;/a&gt;, and a Master&amp;rsquo;s degree in Applied Mathematics in 2017 from the &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.nitw.ac.in/math&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;National Institute of Technology, Warangal, Telangana&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;br&gt;
I earned my Ph.D. in Applied Mathematics in 2025 from the &lt;a href=&#34;https://math.njit.edu&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Department of Mathematical Sciences, New Jersey Institute of Technology&lt;/a&gt;, where I was advised by &lt;a href=&#34;https://roygoodman.net&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Dr. Roy Goodman&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
